The paper discusses the use of RF energy harvesting in wireless networks, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses circuit design (cs.ET), communication protocols (cs.AR), and key design issues (cs.SY) related to RF energy harvesting networks. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of cognitive radio networks (cs.IT) in the development of RF-EHNs.
